'''Al-Campur''' was the administrative [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Sriluur/Legends|Sriluur]]. It was also the birthplace of [[Ak-rev/Legends|Ak-rev]] and contained a monastery dedicated to the [[City/Legends|city's]] patron.<ref name="LoNH">''[[Lords of Nal Hutta]]''</ref>

